OL,3,CLocal pubs 'struggling to stay afloat'
OL,4,Cafter bus stop cut, says MS
OL,6,FTwo Conwy pubs are "struggling to stay
OL,7,Fafloat" after their local bus stop was
OL,8,Fcut following the introduction of the
OL,9,F20mph default speed limit in Wales,
OL,10,Faccording to the local MS.
OL,12,FArriva Buses Wales says it made the
OL,13,Fservice changes to "keep them as
OL,14,Fpunctual as possible". The community
OL,15,Fof Penrhynside has launched a petition
OL,16,Fcalling for the company to reinstate
OL,17,Fits number 14 and 15 services.
