OL,3,CLocal pubs 'struggling to stay afloat'
OL,4,Cafter bus stop cut, says MS
OL,6,FSenedd member for Aberconwy Janet
OL,7,FFinch-Saunders organised a public
OL,8,Fmeeting where local businesses
OL,9,Fdescribed the "financial impact" the
OL,10,Fchanges were having on them. She says
OL,11,Fone of the pubs in the village is now
OL,12,Fconsidering closing a few nights each
OL,13,Fweek.
OL,15,FVillagers also claim they are having
OL,16,Fto walk up and down steep and
OL,17,F"dangerous" hills to reach public
OL,18,Ftransport, with some also having to
OL,19,Fuse expensive taxis to get to and from
OL,20,FLlandudno.
