OL,3,CLocal pubs 'struggling to stay afloat'
OL,4,Cafter bus stop cut, says MS
OL,6,FMs Finch-Saunders is accusing bus
OL,7,Fcompanies of "abandoning" entire
OL,8,Fcommunities and claims the move is
OL,9,Fcontrary to the Welsh Government's
OL,10,Fgoal of creating greener forms of
OL,11,Ftransport.
OL,13,F"Action by Arriva has cut off an
OL,14,Fentire community," she said. "There's
OL,15,Fnow a strong sense of isolation."JAdam
OL,16,FMarshall, Arriva's area head of
OL,17,Fcommercial, has written to Ms Finch-
OL,18,FSaunders saying the decision was
OL,19,Fdriven by electronic ticket machine
OL,20,Fdata showing where and when people
OL,21,Fboard buses.
