OL,3,CLocal pubs 'struggling to stay afloat'
OL,4,Cafter bus stop cut, says MS
OL,6,FThe cancelled Penrynside services mean
OL,7,Fthe nearest bus stops are in Craigside
OL,8,Fand Craig y Don. Arriva Wales has
OL,9,Fblamed the new 20mph speed limit as it
OL,10,Fforced the company to review all its
OL,11,Fservices to "keep them as punctual as
OL,12,Fpossible".JIn the case of services 14
OL,13,Fand 15, the route was changed to
OL,14,F"quicker roads", said Arriva. "Since
OL,15,Fthe changes, punctuality has
OL,16,F"increased significantly", the company
OL,17,Fadded.JMs Finch-Saunders has written
OL,18,Fto Lee Waters, deputy minister for
OL,19,Fclimate change, highlighting local
OL,20,Fanger and the need for urgent action.
OL,21,FShe claimed 20mph was not a
OL,22,Fjustifiable excuse for changing the
OL,23,Ftwo services.
