OL,3,CLocal pubs 'struggling to stay afloat'
OL,4,Cafter bus stop cut, says MS
OL,6,F"Especially when bearing in mind that
OL,7,Fshould the 14 and 15 buses return to
OL,8,FBryn-y-Bia Road, their routes would be
OL,9,Faround 15 metres shorter! The bus
OL,10,Fcompany has completely underestimated
OL,11,Fthe importance of the services to the
OL,12,Fcommunity, and people are now paying
OL,13,Fthe consequences."
OL,15,FIn January ITV Wales reported on the
OL,16,Fimpact a bus service review in
OL,17,FDenbighshire was having on the village
OL,18,Fof Llandegla. Within weeks it was
OL,19,Fpartly reinstated.
